{
  "id": "6656c940808e36001cbd5a12",
  "title": "紅旗破賊非吾事",
  "created": 1716963650,
  "updated": 1716964959,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "6656c940808e36001cbd5a12",
      "text": "紅旗破賊非吾事",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1716963650,
      "updated": 1716963650
    },
    {
      "id": "6656c9445e90c00000d291cd",
      "text": "「劉十九同宿」唐・[白居易]の一節",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1716963650,
      "updated": 1716963650
    },
    {
      "id": "6656c9445e90c00000d291ce",
      "text": " これをもとに[藤原定家]が[紅旗征戎非吾事]と[『明月記』]に残したのが有名",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1716963650,
      "updated": 1716963650
    },
    {
      "id": "6656c9445e90c00000d291cf",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1716963650,
      "updated": 1716963650
    },
    {
      "id": "6656c9445e90c00000d291d0",
      "text": "> 紅旗破賊非吾事",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1716963650,
      "updated": 1716963650
    },
    {
      "id": "6656c9445e90c00000d291d1",
      "text": "> 黄紙除書無我名",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1716963650,
      "updated": 1716963650
    },
    {
      "id": "6656c9445e90c00000d291d2",
      "text": "> 唯共嵩陽劉處士",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1716963650,
      "updated": 1716963650
    },
    {
      "id": "6656c9445e90c00000d291d3",
      "text": "> 圍棋賭酒到天明",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1716963650,
      "updated": 1716963650
    },
    {
      "id": "6656c9445e90c00000d291d4",
      "text": "http://www5a.biglobe.ne.jp/~shici/shi4_08/rs368.htm",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1716963650,
      "updated": 1716963650
    },
    {
      "id": "6656c9445e90c00000d291d5",
      "text": ">紅旗、賊を破るは吾が事に非ず",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1716963650,
      "updated": 1716963650
    },
    {
      "id": "6656c9445e90c00000d291d6",
      "text": ">黄紙、除書に我が名無し",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1716963650,
      "updated": 1716963650
    },
    {
      "id": "6656c9445e90c00000d291d7",
      "text": ">唯だ嵩陽の[劉處士]と共に",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1716963650,
      "updated": 1716963650
    },
    {
      "id": "6656c9445e90c00000d291d8",
      "text": ">棋を圍（かこ）み酒を賭して、天明に至る",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1716963650,
      "updated": 1716963650
    },
    {
      "id": "6656c9445e90c00000d291d9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1716963650,
      "updated": 1716963650
    },
    {
      "id": "6656c9445e90c00000d291da",
      "text": "[https://crd.ndl.go.jp/reference/modules/d3ndlcrdentry/index.php?page=ref_view&id=1000114725 白氏文集の中で「紅旗征戎」の載っている詩がどこにあるか | レファレンス協同データベース]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1716963650,
      "updated": 1716963650
    },
    {
      "id": "6656c9445e90c00000d291db",
      "text": "> 『白楽天全詩集』復刻愛蔵版（佐久節訳註、日本図書センター、1978年）",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1716963650,
      "updated": 1716963650
    },
    {
      "id": "6656c9445e90c00000d291dc",
      "text": "> の第2巻、p696-697に、原詩、読み下し文、字解、題義、詩意が載っている。",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1716963650,
      "updated": 1716963650
    },
    {
      "id": "6656c9445e90c00000d291dd",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1716963650,
      "updated": 1716963650
    },
    {
      "id": "6656c9445e90c00000d291de",
      "text": "語釈",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1716963650,
      "updated": 1716963650
    },
    {
      "id": "6656c9445e90c00000d291df",
      "text": " 紅旗",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1716963650,
      "updated": 1716963650
    },
    {
      "id": "6656c9445e90c00000d291e0",
      "text": "  赤い色の旗。天子、宮廷の象徴として用いられる。",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1716963650,
      "updated": 1716963650
    },
    {
      "id": "6656c9445e90c00000d291e1",
      "text": "  [『和漢朗詠集』]の帝王部に用例あり。",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1716963650,
      "updated": 1716963650
    },
    {
      "id": "6656c9445e90c00000d291e2",
      "text": " [紅旗破賊非吾事]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1716963650,
      "updated": 1716963650
    },
    {
      "id": "6656c9445e90c00000d291e3",
      "text": "  後に[藤原定家]の日記、[『明月記』]に以下の文章を生むもととなった。",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1716963650,
      "updated": 1716963650
    },
    {
      "id": "6656cded5e90c00000d29215",
      "text": "   →[紅旗征戎非吾事]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1716964843,
      "updated": 1716964959
    },
    {
      "id": "6656c9445e90c00000d291ed",
      "text": " 黄紙",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1716963650,
      "updated": 1716963650
    },
    {
      "id": "6656c9445e90c00000d291ee",
      "text": "  > [黄蘗]（きはだ）で染めた黄色い紙。黄蘗は紙を虫の害から防ぐために使い、永く保存を要する経文や天子の勅命などを書く料紙に用いた。黄麻紙。黄麻。おうし。（日国）",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1716963650,
      "updated": 1716963960
    },
    {
      "id": "6656c9445e90c00000d291ef",
      "text": " 除書",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1716963650,
      "updated": 1716963650
    },
    {
      "id": "6656c9445e90c00000d291f0",
      "text": "  > 役人に任ずることを知らせる書き付け。任命通知。辞令。（新撰漢和辞典）",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1716963650,
      "updated": 1716963650
    },
    {
      "id": "6656c9445e90c00000d291f1",
      "text": " 勅命にも、辞令にも、私の名前はない＝戦地に出る仕事の任にはついていない。指名も受けていない。",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1716963650,
      "updated": 1716963650
    },
    {
      "id": "6656c9445e90c00000d291f2",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1716963650,
      "updated": 1716963650
    },
    {
      "id": "6656c9445e90c00000d291f3",
      "text": " 嵩陽",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1716963650,
      "updated": 1716963650
    },
    {
      "id": "6656c9445e90c00000d291f4",
      "text": "  [嵩山]の南側（陽）のことだろうか？[cFQ2f7LRuLYP.icon]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1716963650,
      "updated": 1716963650
    },
    {
      "id": "6656c9445e90c00000d291f5",
      "text": "   陽は南をあらわすことがある。山陽地方と山陰地方の関係を思い出せ。",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1716963650,
      "updated": 1716963650
    },
    {
      "id": "6656c9445e90c00000d291f6",
      "text": " 劉處士",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1716963650,
      "updated": 1716963650
    },
    {
      "id": "6656c9445e90c00000d291f7",
      "text": "  劉十九のことか。",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1716963650,
      "updated": 1716963650
    },
    {
      "id": "6656c9445e90c00000d291f8",
      "text": "  白氏文集にときどき名がみえるらしい。",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1716963650,
      "updated": 1716963650
    },
    {
      "id": "6656c9445e90c00000d291f9",
      "text": "   巻十七、薔薇が開いて春酒が熟したので、劉十九、張大夫、崔二十四を招いて酒を飲んだときの歌",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1716963650,
      "updated": 1716963650
    },
    {
      "id": "6656c9445e90c00000d291fa",
      "text": "  処士は、民間にあって士官していない人のことを指す。",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1716963650,
      "updated": 1716963650
    },
    {
      "id": "6656c9445e90c00000d291fb",
      "text": "   > 清原国賢書写本荘子抄〔１５３０〕一「家に居て奉公せぬ男を処士と云ぞ」",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1716963650,
      "updated": 1716963650
    },
    {
      "id": "6656c9445e90c00000d291fc",
      "text": " 圍棋",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1716963650,
      "updated": 1716963650
    },
    {
      "id": "6656c9445e90c00000d291fd",
      "text": "  [囲碁]。",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1716963650,
      "updated": 1716963650
    },
    {
      "id": "6656c9445e90c00000d291fe",
      "text": "   碁の起源は四千年とも言われており、[堯舜]の時代から伝わったという伝承があるらしい。",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1716963650,
      "updated": 1716963650
    },
    {
      "id": "6656c9445e90c00000d291ff",
      "text": "   [琴棋書画]のひとつであり、[士君子]の技芸をして尊ばれた。",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1716963650,
      "updated": 1716963650
    },
    {
      "id": "6656c9445e90c00000d29200",
      "text": " 酒を賭ける",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1716963650,
      "updated": 1716963650
    },
    {
      "id": "6656c9445e90c00000d29201",
      "text": "  [遊仙窟]に用例があるらしい",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1716963650,
      "updated": 1716963650
    },
    {
      "id": "6656c9445e90c00000d29202",
      "text": "   東洋文庫が検索で引っかかった",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1716963650,
      "updated": 1716963650
    },
    {
      "id": "6656c9445e90c00000d29203",
      "text": " 天明",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1716963650,
      "updated": 1716963650
    },
    {
      "id": "6656c9445e90c00000d29204",
      "text": "  明け方のこと。",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1716963650,
      "updated": 1716963650
    },
    {
      "id": "6656c9445e90c00000d29205",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1716963650,
      "updated": 1716963650
    },
    {
      "id": "6656c9445e90c00000d29206",
      "text": "現代語訳",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1716963650,
      "updated": 1716963650
    },
    {
      "id": "6656c9445e90c00000d29207",
      "text": " 紅旗、賊を破るは吾が事に非ず",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1716963650,
      "updated": 1716963650
    },
    {
      "id": "6656c9445e90c00000d29208",
      "text": "  天子の旗の下、賊を打ちのめすのは私の仕事じゃありません",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1716963650,
      "updated": 1716963650
    },
    {
      "id": "6656c9445e90c00000d29209",
      "text": " 黄紙、除書に我が名無し",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1716963650,
      "updated": 1716963650
    },
    {
      "id": "6656c9445e90c00000d2920a",
      "text": "  勅も辞令にも名前はないし",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1716963650,
      "updated": 1716963650
    },
    {
      "id": "6656c9445e90c00000d2920b",
      "text": " 唯だ嵩陽の劉處士と共に",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1716963650,
      "updated": 1716963650
    },
    {
      "id": "6656c9445e90c00000d2920c",
      "text": "  やるべきことといえば、嵩陽の劉くんと一緒に",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1716963650,
      "updated": 1716963650
    },
    {
      "id": "6656c9445e90c00000d2920d",
      "text": " 棋を圍（かこ）み酒を賭して、天明に至る",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1716963650,
      "updated": 1716963650
    },
    {
      "id": "6656c9445e90c00000d2920e",
      "text": "  囲碁をしつつ酒を賭け、そのまま夜明けまでいることさ",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1716963650,
      "updated": 1716963650
    }
  ]
}